<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Inkra Data Export is Ready</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .download-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .download-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: #4F46E5;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .download-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .download-text {
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .expires-warning {
      background: #FEF3C7;
      border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .what-included {
      background: #F3F4F6;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .what-included h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .what-included ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .what-included li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">Inkra</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>Your Data Export is Ready!</h2>
    
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    
    <p>Your complete Inkra data export has been prepared and is ready for download. This includes all your interview projects, audio recordings, transcripts, and account data.</p>

    <div class="download-section">
      <div class="download-text">Click below to download your data:</div>
      <a href="<%= @download_url %>" class="download-button">Download My Inkra Data</a>
    </div>

    <div class="expires-warning">
      <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This download link expires on <strong><%= @expires_at %></strong>. Make sure to download your data before this date.
    </div>

    <div class="what-included">
      <h3>What's included in your export:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>CSV Data Files</strong> - Your structured data in spreadsheet format</li>
        <li><strong>Audio Recordings</strong> - All your interview audio files</li>
        <li><strong>Transcripts</strong> - Text versions of your interviews</li>
        <li><strong>Account Settings</strong> - Your preferences and configuration</li>
        <li><strong>Support History</strong> - Any feedback or support interactions</li>
        <li><strong>README File</strong> - Instructions for understanding your data</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>The export is provided as a ZIP file containing organized folders with your data. You can open CSV files in Excel, Google Sheets, or any spreadsheet application.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions about your export or need help accessing your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@inkra.app">support@inkra.app</a>.</p>

    <p>Thank you for using Inkra to capture your stories!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Inkra Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %> at your request.</p>
    <p>Inkra - Capture your voice, preserve your story</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>